The best desi food you will ever have in New York. I ordered vegetarian curry platter with Onion Naan and Kheer. The food was so amazing that I stocked up for 2 days. I can only imagine that vegetarian food was so delicious it will be a real treat for non vegetarian food lovers. Definitely the best desi restaurant in New York. The service is equally brilliant as the staff is so friendly that they would recommend food as per your mood and taste. I love spicy food and the staff made sure my food had the right amount of spice to get the flavor of Indian food. Zaiqa is the right name for the restaurant as it truly brings in the flavor of Indian, Pakistani and Bangladeshi food. Do not miss the Kheer whenever you visit this place it will definitely be one of the best desserts you have ever had.
